headline: Palantir and Booz Allen Hamilton, Shopify, Uber: Market Minute
summary: Yahoo Finance host Akiko Fujita highlights three of this morning's top stories and trending stocks. Palantir (PLTR) shares are rising after signing a new AI partnership with defense contractor Booz Allen Hamilton (BAH). Shopify (SHOP) gets an upgrade to a Buy rating from Loop Capital Markets analysts. Uber (UBER) will team up with Chinese robotaxi operator WeRide in a move to expand services to Abu Dhabi in 2025. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Wealth here. This post was written by Luke Carberry Mogan.
